How We Recovered Over N1billion From A Civil Servant In One Week—EFCC Chairman
0 Comments
3 Weeks Ago “We have recovered over N1 billion sitting in the account of a civil servant last week.” Bawa however refused to mention the name of the individual civil servant. Speaking to SaharaReporters on Thursday, a source at the anti-graft agency identified the civil servant as a Permanent Secretary working with Fashola. “The civil servant the chairman was talking about is the Permanent Secretary working directly with Fashola,” the source said.